description: Truly one of a kind, this stunning condo is located in a beautifully converted historic church ideally located just one block from the Red Line T and with quick access to I90 and I93. Rich with character, the home features soaring original arches, vibrant stained-glass windows, and unique architectural details that create a dramatic and inspiring living space. Inside, you'll find gleaming hardwood floors, central AC, and an open layout that lives much larger than expected. The updated kitchen is outfitted with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a breakfast bar. Two full bathrooms, in unit laundry, ample closet space, and a deeded parking space complete this incredible unit. Don’t miss a chance to own this unique condo that blends historical architecture and modern living.
